<p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0;">Fort Pitt July the 2d. 1780. G.f. Linctot</p>
<p style="text-align: right;">Fort Pitt July 3rd. 1780</p>
<p>I certify that to the best of my knowledge Major Lanctot has given the above Articles to the Delaware Indians with a view to serve the United States.</p>
<div class="closer">
<div class="signed-multiple">
    <p class="signed multiple"><span class="hi-small-caps" style="font-variant: small-caps;">Daniel Brodhead</span><br/>Colo. commandg. W.D.</p>
  </div>
</div>
